cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.RO

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision, specifically on training and testing object detectors using virtual images. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of deep learning models, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the performance of the models, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.GR (Graphics). Finally, the paper discusses the potential applications of the virtual dataset in robotics, which could fall under cs.RO (Robotics).
